The paper deals with a wiretap channel, which is a topic in information theory (cs.IT) and network security (cs.CR). The use of compute-and-forward decoding and lattice alignment suggests a focus on signal processing and coding (cs.MM), while the use of i.i.d. random codes suggests a focus on networking and communication (cs.NI).
